description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of a mixed use development of three main buildings of between six and fifteen-storeys, comprising 252 units of residential accommodation, hotel accommodation and associated facilities, Business Centre (Class B1a), heliport facilities with visual control room for adjacent heliport, and commercial uses including shops, financial and professional services, restaurants, cafs, pubs, bars and business use (within classes A1, A2, A3, A4 and B1), riverside walk, open space, basement car parking (353 spaces) and ground level servicing with widening of private road and provision of drop off lay-by.
